data.title: Dominique Hourani
data.meta_description: Posts about Dominique Hourani written by lebanesecelebritynews
data.text:
Dominique Hourani shared the above photo of her on Instagram while she was busting her booty in the gym at The Address Dubai Mall, United Arab Emirates.

Along the pic she wrote, “Sports is happiness #gym #time no #limits for #happy #times at The Address Dubai Mall.”

The 34-year-old singer looked hot in light pink shorts along with a dark blue shirt that showed off her sexy slimmed body.

She’s just perfect the way she is!

Dominique Hourani shared the above photo of her on Instagram before attending the concert of the Emirati singer Ahlam Shamsi and the Saudi singer Mohamed Abdo, at Dubai Shopping Festival, United Arab Emirates.

Along the pic she wrote, “Going to attend the #huge #event #Ahlam the #queen and #giant #mohamedabdo today in #uae #dubai lovely #event.”

The 34-year-old singer looked stylish in black leather leggings along with a white top and a black glitter jacket.

We’re loving those black heels by Dolce & Gabbana.

Check below the dress of Ahlam Shamsi at the concert:

Those Prada sunglasses look adorable on her! What do you think?

Dominique Hourani posted the above photo of her on Instagram and captioned it, “Love #fashion love #prada #glasses.”

The 34-year-old singer looked beautiful in white and pink striped leggings along with a pink shirt. What a refreshing look!

Wow– look at those hot toned abs!

Dominique Hourani shared the above photo of her on Instagram while she was celebrating her friend’s wedding Hossam Labash and Sarab Ghanem. Congrats!

Along the pic she wrote, “My lovers, my friends and my fans… You’re always in my heart and eyes #happy like never before #enjoy every moment.”

We’re glad to see her feeling better this time!

The singer looked gorgeous in a mini pink skirt along with a cream colored cropped top that showed off her sexy abs.

Aww– we are in love with the Indian outfit!

Dominique Hourani posted the above photo of her on Instagram while she was rehearsing for New Year’s Eve concert that she will be hosting with the Lebanese singer Amir Yazbeck, at Plaza Palace, in Tabarja, Lebanon.

Along the pic she wrote, “Rehearsing for my New Year’s Eve concerts tomorow #star #dominique on #stage #singer #dominiqueh #happy #Arabian #spirit.”

The Lebanese singer looked beautiful in jeans along with a purple shirt, a fury vest and black boots. Adorable!

Dominique Hourani posted the above photo of her on Instagram while she appeared on the December issue of “Nesf El Donya” Egyptian magazine.

The 34-year-old Lebanese singer looked gorgeous in a cream colored skirt along with a cropped top. Adorable!

During the magazine interview, Dominique said, “My beauty is natural and i didn’t do any plastic surgeries.”

Aww– we have no doubt! She’s beautiful by nature indeed! We love her!

Aww– short hair and black locks! Thats one complete transformation right there! We love it!

Dominique Hourani posted the above photo of her on Instagram as she have recently chopped off her hair and dyed it black. How cool is that!

Along the pic she wrote, ” Did you like my short hair? My clothes by this boutique @elegante__ love.”

The singer looked gothic glam in an all black outfit along with her new black short hair. We adore the new look!

Dominique Hourani looked stunning while walking the red carpet at Dubai International Film Festival, in Dubai, United Arab Emirates.

Regarding the event she wrote, “Amazing event with the most famous celebrities . Dubai film festival was such a productive event ! Love you uae ! It was good to catch up with my celebrity frnds.”

The 34-year-old singer looked flawless in a light pink silk dress designed by Said Kobeissy along with a lovely golden bag by Louis Vuitton.

She knows how to work it on the red carpet!

Aww– how cute is that minnie mouse piece on her head!

Dominique Hourani shared the above photo of her on Instagram while she was having a halloween party with her friends.

Along the pic she wrote,

Happy Halloween @queen_maryoum #dominique #Dominiqueh #costumes #minnie_mouse.”

The 34-year-old singer looked hot in a mini black ripped dress that showed off her sexy slim legs.

Wow– halloween is on fire this year!

Aww– it looks like she loves animals so much! Before she posed with a champion horse and now with a husky!

Dominique Hourani shared the above throwback photo of her on Instagram while she was enjoying the snow with a husky dog in Faraya, Lebanon.

Along the pic she wrote, “Love #snow #photos With #husky #dog #winter #faraya #lebanon #ski #fun.”

The singer looked adorable in red sweat pants and jacket along with white boots.

How cute are they!
